# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values:
# Never commit `.env` — it contains secrets.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Required — wallet private key used to sign Polymarket CLOB requests
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 64 hex characters, with or without a 0x prefix.
# This must be the key for the wallet that holds (or controls) your trading USDC.
#
# Example (fake — do not use):
# POLYMARKET_PRIVATE_KEY=0x0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef
POLYMARKET_PRIVATE_KEY=

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional — Polymarket proxy / funder wallet address
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Leave blank if you trade directly from an EOA (MetaMask, hardware wallet, etc.).
#
# Set this if you signed up on polymarket.com with email / social login.
# In that case your USDC sits in a Polymarket proxy wallet, not the EOA above.
# Use your Polymarket profile address (the funder shown in account settings).
#
# When set, the bot uses signature type 2 (proxy) and reads balance from this address.
#
# Example (fake — do not use):
# PROXY_WALLET_ADDRESS=0xAbCdEf1234567890AbCdEf1234567890AbCdEf12
# PROXY_WALLET_ADDRESS=
